description: States members vote in favour of adapting the "delay, contain, shield" strategy.
title: Coronavirus: Jersey aims for 'very low levels' in updated strategy
title_page: Coronavirus: Jersey aims for 'very low levels' in updated strategy - BBC News
maintext: "The challenge we now face as an island community is to continue to navigate through the pandemic in a way that keeps cases at a very low level, causes least harm overall and maximises wellbeing."
